Title: 'Host groups' view: Add coloring for host states
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 2.2.0b1
Date: 1656407475
Class: fix

In the view "Host groups" host state cells were not colored according to their state. This is fixed, so now whenever there's at least one occurence of the given host state for the given host group, the table cell is colored. This behavior now matches that of the service state cells again.
